quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,"Ashe, ba ka ga yadda Ubangijin ka Ya aikata ga mutanen giwa* ba"
  105,2,"Ashe, bai sanya kaidin su a cikin ɓata ba"
  105,3,"Kuma Ya sako, a kansu, wasu tsuntsãye, jama'a-jama'a"
  105,4,Suna jifar su da wasu duwatsu na yumɓun wuta
  105,5,Sa'an nan Ya sanya su kamar karmami wanda aka cinye